@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
    Layout = null;
}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Raj Dairy Pro - Privacy Policy</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }
        body { background: #f8fafc; }
        h1, h2, h3 { color: #0f172a; }
        .policy-card { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container py-5">
        <div class="policy-card">
            <div class="text-center mb-5">
                <div class="mx-auto mb-3" style="width:60px;height:60px;border-radius:16px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f172a,#334155);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;">
                    <i class="bi bi-droplet-fill text-white" style="font-size:1.5rem;"></i>
                </div>
                <h1 class="fw-bold">Raj Dairy Pro</h1>
                <p class="text-muted">Privacy Policy</p>
                <small class="text-muted">Last updated: @DateTime.Today.ToString("dd MMMM yyyy")</small>
            </div>

            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm p-4 p-md-5" style="border-radius:16px;">

                <h2 class="fw-bold mb-3">1. Introduction</h2>
                <p>Raj Dairy Pro ("we", "our", "us") is a dairy management application designed to help dairy businesses manage their daily operations including milk collection, partner management, orders, and financial records. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information.</p>

                <h2 class="fw-bold mb-3 mt-4">2. Information We Collect</h2>
                <p>We collect the following types of information:</p>
                <h3 class="fw-semibold fs-5">2.1 Admin User Information</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Full name, username, and password for admin login</li>
                    <li>Mobile number (optional)</li>
                    <li>Dairy/business name</li>
                    <li>Profile photo (optional)</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="fw-semibold fs-5">2.2 Partner/Farmer Information</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Partner name and mobile number</li>
                    <li>Address (optional)</li>
                    <li>Partner type (Supplier/Buyer)</li>
                    <li>Access code for partner portal</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="fw-semibold fs-5">2.3 Business Data</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Milk collection records (quantity, fat%, SNF%, rates)</li>
                    <li>Transaction records (payments, receipts)</li>
                    <li>Order and subscription details</li>
                    <li>Expense records</li>
                    <li>Ghee production and dairy product records</li>
                    <li>UPI ID and QR code for payment (optional)</li>
                </ul>

                <h2 class="fw-bold mb-3 mt-4">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
                <p>Your information is used solely for:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Managing dairy operations (milk collection, orders, payments)</li>
                    <li>Generating reports and analytics for your business</li>
                    <li>Facilitating communication between admin and partners via WhatsApp</li>
                    <li>Processing payments through UPI</li>
                    <li>Providing partner portal access for account viewing</li>
                </ul>

                <h2 class="fw-bold mb-3 mt-4">4. Data Storage</h2>
                <p>All data is stored securely in <strong>Google Sheets</strong> via the Google Sheets API. This means:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Data is stored on Google's secure cloud infrastructure</li>
                    <li>Data is protected by Google's security measures</li>
                    <li>The dairy admin has full control and ownership of their data</li>
                    <li>Data can be accessed, exported, or deleted at any time by the admin</li>
                </ul>

                <h2 class="fw-bold mb-3 mt-4">5. Data Sharing</h2>
                <p>We <strong>do not</strong> share, sell, or transfer your personal data to any third parties. Your data is only accessible to:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Admin users of your dairy (based on their role permissions)</li>
                    <li>Partners/farmers (only their own data, read-only via access code)</li>
                    <li>Google (as the cloud storage provider, governed by Google's Privacy Policy)</li>
                </ul>

                <h2 class="fw-bold mb-3 mt-4">6. Data Security</h2>
                <p>We implement the following security measures:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Password-protected admin access</li>
                    <li>Role-based access control (SuperAdmin, Admin, Operator)</li>
                    <li>Data isolation - each admin sees only their own data</li>
                    <li>CSRF protection on all forms</li>
                    <li>Session-based authentication with 8-hour timeout</li>
                    <li>Partner portal is read-only - partners cannot modify any data</li>
                </ul>

                <h2 class="fw-bold mb-3 mt-4">7. Your Rights</h2>
                <p>As a user, you have the right to:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Access</strong> - View all your stored data at any time</li>
                    <li><strong>Export</strong> - Download your data in CSV format</li>
                    <li><strong>Modify</strong> - Update or correct your information</li>
                    <li><strong>Delete</strong> - Request deletion of your data</li>
                    <li><strong>Portability</strong> - Export data and move to another service</li>
                </ul>

                <h2 class="fw-bold mb-3 mt-4">8. Children's Privacy</h2>
                <p>This application is designed for business use and is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.</p>

                <h2 class="fw-bold mb-3 mt-4">9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
                <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected on this page with an updated "Last updated" date.</p>

                <h2 class="fw-bold mb-3 mt-4">10. Contact Us</h2>
                <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or your data, please contact us:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>App:</strong> Raj Dairy Pro</li>
                    <li><strong>Website:</strong> rajdairy.onrender.com</li>
                    <li><strong>Email:</strong> rajrevclerx&#64;gmail.com</li>
                </ul>

            </div>

            <div class="text-center mt-4">
                <a href="/" class="text-primary text-decoration-none"><i class="bi bi-arrow-left me-1"></i>Back to App</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</body>
</html>
